<item>
            <title>[LU-1006] Test failure on test suite conf-sanity</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1006</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Peter Jones &amp;lt;pjones@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/139efa48-410a-11e1-972d-5254004bbbd3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/139efa48-410a-11e1-972d-5254004bbbd3&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
